ActAppropriation Act No. 1, 2013-2014
PrecisAppointment of DAVID ANGELL as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Federal Republic of Somalia, with residence in Nairobi; JOHN BARRETT as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Slovak Republic, with residence in Vienna; CHRISTOPHER COOTER as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Equatorial Guinea, with residence in Abuja; LOUIS DE LORIMIER as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Niger, with residence in Bamako; and RICHARD HANLEY as non-resident Consul General of Canada in Anguilla and as non-resident Consul General of Canada in the British Virgin Islands, with residence in Bridgetown.
